# Blog Punctuation

Do not use em dashes (`—`, U+2014) in blog articles.

Use a spaced hyphen instead: ` - `

## Examples

```
❌ Anthropic launches Fable 5 — the same underlying model
✅ Anthropic launches Fable 5 - the same underlying model

❌ Pricing drops to $10 — less than half
✅ Pricing drops to $10 - less than half
```

When editing or writing content under `content/`, replace any `—` with ` - `.
